Wind Rider

Blocks wind moves. Attack is boosted from Tailwind or when hit by a wind move.

Affected Moves

The following moves are affected by this ability.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Aeroblast 5 100 95 A vortex of air is shot at the target to inflict damage. Critical hits land more easily.
Air Cutter 25 60 95 The user launches razor-like wind to slash opposing Pokémon. Critical hits land more easily.
Air Slash 15 75 95 The user attacks with a blade of air that slices even the sky. It may make the target flinch.
Bleakwind Storm 10 100 80 The user attacks with savagely cold winds. It may lower Speed.
Blizzard 5 110 70 A howling blizzard strikes opposing Pokémon. This may also leave them with frostbite.
Dual Wingbeat 10 40 90 The user slams the target with its wings. The target is hit twice in a row.
Fairy Wind 30 40 100 The user stirs up a fairy wind and strikes the target with it.
Glaciate 10 65 95 The user blows freezing cold air at opposing Pokémon. This lowers their Speed stats.
Gust 35 40 100 A gust of wind is whipped up by wings and launched at the target to inflict damage.
Heat Wave 10 100 90 The user exhales hot breath on opposing Pokémon. This may also leave them with a burn.
Hurricane 10 110 70 The user attacks by wrapping its opponent in a fierce wind. This may also confuse it.
Icy Wind 15 55 95 The user attacks with a gust of chilled air. This also lowers opposing Pokémon's Speed stats.
Ominous Wind 5 60 100 The target is blasted with a gust of repulsive wind. It may also raise all the user's stats.
Petal Blizzard 15 90 100 The user stirs up a violent petal blizzard and attacks everything around it.
Powder Snow 25 40 100 The user attacks with a chilling gust of powdery snow. This may also frostbite.
Razor Wind 10 70 100 Blades of wind hit opposing Pokémon. Critical hits land more easily.
Sandsear Storm 10 100 80 Wraps the foe in searingly hot sand. It may inflict a burn.
Sandstorm 10 — — A five-turn sandstorm is summoned to hurt all except Rock, Ground, and Steel types.
Silver Wind 5 60 100 Powdery scales blown by wind attack the target. This may also raise all the user's stats.
Simoom 15 80 100 A violent wind that hurls sand and rocks at opposing foes. It may lower their Sp. Def stats.
Springtide Storm 5 100 80 The user wraps the foe in fierce winds. It may lower the target's Attack.
Steel Wing 25 70 90 The target is hit with wings of steel. This may also raise the user's Defense stat.
Tailwind 15 — — The user whips up a whirlwind that ups its and its allies' Speed stats for four turns.
Twister 20 40 100 A vicious twister is whipped up to tear at opposing Pokémon. It may also make them flinch.
Whirlwind 20 — — The target is blown away and switched. This ends a battle against a single wild Pokémon.
Wildbolt Storm 10 100 80 The user attacks with a thunderous tempest. It may paralyze.
Wing Attack 35 60 100 The target is struck with large, imposing wings spread wide to inflict damage.
